            <title>[PDFBOX-3517] [Patch] CCITTFactory.createFromFile methods do not release lock on source file</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3517</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using CCITTFactory.createFromFile methods, a RandomAccessFile is created on the source file, but never closed.&lt;br/&gt;
On Windows, this locks the file. I haven&apos;t had the time yet to test on Linux.&lt;br/&gt;
I have prepared a patch in GitHub, will post as soon as it&apos;s pushed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
